preference.name: Mat1UsesMaterial.mat1mass.FORMATSTRING
preference.preference_description: Specifies the format used to display the value of the property "mat1mass" for objects of type "Mat1UsesMaterial". The default value is "##.####", where "#" indicates a digit. It will be displayed if it adds to the accuracy of the number but not if it is a leading zero or a zero at the end of a decimal.
